{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we reported in, and we were given-- had billets-- nice, two men in a room, they-- good food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had been getting pretty good food, by the way, which was a whole different ballgame than in France-- terrible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes, yeah, when we were moving so much, it would be rare to get a hot meal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It would be rare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The eggs were always powdered eggs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The milk was always powdered milk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The meat was-- a lot of times was mutton or goat-- goat meat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't handle it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never could, and I still can't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were eat-- you were eating-- we were moving so much that they couldn't supply us with what they normally would in an Air Corp unit-- in their Air Force unit.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is after D-day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just you know-- everybody was going full bore to get to Germany to end the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and then we were unfortunately-- we weren't based in one place long enough for the food guys to catch up with us where we can sit down and have mashed potatoes and chicken fried steaks and things like that-- once in a while, but very seldom.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when we got to Gelnhausen, we had our own-- just our squadron had our own mess.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were getting food from-- eggs, for example, and vegetables, radishes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll never forget the first time I had a fresh radish from the farmers around there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, with-- our mess sergeant would go out there with a truck and a whole bunch of coffee and candy bars and what have you and come back with a truck full of fresh vegetables.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And boy, I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- and we had got some venison that we killed ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
